text: Hello, good morning :slightly_smiling_face:
Hi! Good morning!. How may I assist you? :slightly_smiling_face:
I am looking for some hotels in Ooty .:smiley:
These are some of the hotels in Ooty :slightly_smiling_face: .
These are good:slightly_smiling_face: but I am looking something on the hilly area.
Oh!! I am glad you asked. :stuck_out_tongue: There are plenty of hotels in hilly areas. Let me get you that!
The third image looks beautiful:heart_eyes: Can you show some more similar to this?
Happy to hear that you liked this hotel! I have some more of this kind. :stuck_out_tongue_winking_eye:
I couldn't find many but here are some nearby and of the same kind. :slightly_smiling_face:
Ohh I guess I would like to check the previous hotel only:frowning:. Can you show the rooms?
I apologize for that! please have a look at the rooms from this hotel. :wink:
Can you show some more of the 2nd type having good scenic view:slightly_smiling_face:
There is only one room left other than that! Rest all others are booked. This is hotel is in huge demand now :wink:.
Can you tell the rating of the hotel?
The customer rating for this hotel is 3.5 :neutral_face: for their service and for food and facility it is rated 4.0. :slightly_smiling_face:
Is there swimming pool available in the hotel?
Yeah, there is a swimming pool available at the backyard. :wink:
Okay but it doesn't seems to be very clean and big :disappointed:. Do they have a restaurant as well?
Please don't be worried! I am here to help you. Yes! they have their own restaurant facility. :stuck_out_tongue:
Wow its perfect atleast we won't be hungry:grinning:.
I'm happy for you! Do you want to book this hotel? :thinking_face:
Can you tell the distance from the station and if early check-in is possible?
The distance from the railway station is around 15km and early check-in is possible but only after 8.00 am. :slightly_smiling_face:
Its seems really far from the station:disappointed: but I do like the early check-in advantage.
There is not much traffic in this area and at any time cabs are available so distance won't affect your plans! :relaxed:
That is comforting:blush: Can you tell the price of the rooms?
The room is for 2000/- Rs per night and about 3 people can comfortably stay in there! :slightly_smiling_face:
Wow its affordable:heart_eyes:. Can you tell the check-in and check-out timings?
You can check-in from 10.00 am onwards 12pm is the checkout timing. I hope that it is fine by you!
Yes that is perfect:heart_eyes: Thanks for the help:blush:
You are always welcome! :star-struck:
